title: Rebecca Adlington talks swimming, returning to the East Village and having mo... - Western Telegraph
text:
Olympic gold medallist Rebecca Adlington has described returning to the East Village, the former Athletes' Village during the 2012 Olympic and Paralympic Games, as amazing. "Before going I was thinking, 'gosh am I going to remember it?' because it feels so long ago, but it was amazing to go back and see it all finished."
 Western Telegraph.
